Description: local network client daemon, Kotlin/Compose desktop controller, and terminal dashboard
 clambhook provides a local network client daemon, HTTP control API, and a
 Kotlin/Compose Multiplatform desktop controller plus a terminal dashboard. It
 includes a private license helper used by the desktop app for trial and license
 activation against the hosted store backend.
